heroes.name: npc_dota_hero_dark_seer
heroes.bio_loc:
Fast when he needs to be, and a cunning strategist, Ish'Kafel the Dark Seer requires no edged weapons to vanquish his enemies, relying instead on the strength of his powerful mind. His talent lies in his ability to maneuver the fight to his advantage. Hailing from a place he calls 'The Land behind the wall,' Dark Seer remains an outsider here--a warrior from a realm beyond the veil of this reality.

Once a great general among his people, and a valiant defender of the god-king Damathryx, Dark Seer's army was wiped out by a much larger force in the final days of the Great Boundaries War. Facing certain defeat, he made one last desperate act: he led the enemy forces into the maze between the walls. At the last moment, just before capture, he crossed over--then sealed the walls forever in an explosive release of dark energy. When the dust settled, he saw that he had saved his people but found himself blinking at the sun of a different world, with no way to return. Now he is committed to proving his worth as a military strategist, and vows to show that he's the greatest tactician this strange new world has ever seen.
heroes.hype_loc: Versatile and strategic, Dark Seer excels at manipulating the positions of his enemies. Vacuuming foes into the attacks of his allies, he can turn enemy strength against itself by pulling foes through his replicating wall.
heroes.npe_desc_loc: Pulls and manipulates his enemies' positions

facets.description_loc: Dark Seer also gains Attack Speed from Intelligence.
facets.name: dark_seer_atkspd

facets.description_loc: Dark Seer moves faster when near other heroes.
facets.name: dark_seer_movespd

abilities.name: dark_seer_vacuum
abilities.desc_loc: Dark Seer creates a vacuum over the target area that sucks in enemy units, disrupting them and dealing damage.
abilities.lore_loc: Ish'Kafel modifies the center of gravity to a place of his choosing.
notes_loc: Pulls units over %duration% seconds before dealing damage.
Trees near the center of the vacuum will be destroyed.

abilities.name: dark_seer_ion_shell
abilities.desc_loc: Surrounds the target unit with a bristling shield that damages enemy units in an area around it.
abilities.lore_loc: The Dark Seer slices holes into the 'Land Behind the Wall,' causing prismatic energy to seep forth.
notes_loc: Deals small amounts of damage in %tick_interval% second intervals.
Doesn't damage the target it is cast on.
If cast on a unit that already has Ion Shell, the new Shell replaces the old one.
abilities.shard_loc: When Ion Shell is cast on an enemy, it slows them for %enemy_target_slow%%%, the radius is increased by %enemy_target_bonus_radius% and Ion Shell's cooldown is reduced by %enemy_target_cooldown_reduction%s. The enemy is also pulled at a rate of %pull_strength% units toward any other unit affected by Ion Shell.

abilities.name: dark_seer_surge
abilities.desc_loc: Charges a target friendly unit with power, giving it a brief burst of phased movement speed. Allows the unit to reach maximum movement speed and cannot be slowed.
abilities.lore_loc: Ish'Kafel once used his speed of mind to navigate the maze between the walls.
notes_loc: Units with Surge cannot be slowed unless the Surge effect is removed.
abilities.shard_loc: Surged units leave behind a %trail_radius% radius trail that lasts %trail_duration%s, slows enemies around it by %trail_move_slow%%% and deals %trail_damage% damage per second in %trail_damage_interval%s intervals. Can be put on alt-cast to disable the trail.

abilities.name: dark_seer_normal_punch
abilities.desc_loc: Passive ability. Causes Dark Seer's next attack on a hero to have True Strike, knock a replica out of the victim, damaging and stunning them based on how far Dark Seer has moved in the past %recent_duration% seconds. Max power is reached after %max_distance% distance moved.

abilities.name: dark_seer_mental_fortitude
abilities.desc_loc: Dark Seer's Intelligence cannot be lower than either his Strength or Agility.
notes_loc: If his Strength or Agility are higher, he gains Bonus Intelligence to match them.

abilities.name: dark_seer_wall_of_replica
abilities.desc_loc: Raises a wall of warping light that slows, damages, and creates replicas of any enemy hero who crosses it. Enemy replicas serve at the Dark Seer's will. Replicas last until they are destroyed, or until the wall's duration ends.
abilities.lore_loc: The Dark Seer, while unable to return to his natural realm, can channel part of the prismatic wall with powerful strength of mind, sowing confusion amongst enemy ranks.
notes_loc: Doesn't create illusions from other illusions.
There cannot be more than one illusion per player per wall.
Wall of Replica will not slow spell-immune enemies.

abilities.name: dark_seer_quick_wit
abilities.desc_loc: Dark Seer also gains Attack Speed from Intelligence.
notes_loc: Dark Seer gains %int_to_atkspd% Attack Speed from each point of Intelligence.

abilities.name: dark_seer_heart_of_battle
abilities.desc_loc: Dark Seer moves faster when near other heroes.
notes_loc: Dark Seer gains %movement_speed_pct%%% of the movement speed of heroes within %radius% radius. Base movement speed reduced.
